All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Action
This is an Action interface that represents an action that can be executed by a user in the booking system.
ActionCapable
Interface for objects that can perform actions.
AddBalanceAction
This is an AddBalanceAction class that represents an action to add balance to a user's account.
AddBookingAction
This is an AddBookingAction class that represents an action to add a booking to the booking system.
ApplePay
This class implements the Payment interface and is used to process payments using Apple Pay
Application
Main class for the application.
Booking
This is a Booking class that represents a booking with a vehicle.
BookingSystem
A Class for the Booking System.
ConfirmAction
This is a ConfirmAction class that represents an action to confirm bookings in the booking system.
DisplayBookingAction
Action to display the bookings of a user.
EngineType
Enum for the type of engine a vehicle has (Petrol, Diesel and Electric).
ExitAction
Action to exit the system.
GooglePay
This class implements the Payment interface and is used to process payments using Google Pay
Menu
Class for the Menu.
Payment
This interface is used to define the methods that must be implemented by a payment method
RemoveBookingAction
Action to remove a booking from the booking system.
Sedan
A Class for Sedan vehicles.
SUV
A Class for SUV vehicles.
Truck
A Class for Truck vehicles.
User
This is a User class that represents a user with a balance, a list of bookings, and a status indicating if the user is done.
Utility
Utility class for the application.
Vehicle
Class for the Vehicle.
